Diagram 2 (Shortsighted)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is shortsighted for white to push at 1.
\par
\par Black naturally blocks with 2.
\par
\par If white cuts at 3, black plays 4. It's spilt milk now.
\par
\par }
