Diagram 3 (Mistake)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18 .
\par It's a mistake for white to cut at 1.
\par
\par When black plays dansu at 2, you are mistaken if you think you can cross under at 3.
\par
\par After black captures white's stones with 4, there is no move left for white.
\par
\par Up to B6, black lives beautifully.
\par }
